    "Only 32.8% of the studies incorporate psychotherapy theories in their methodological approach.",
    "Notably, emerging therapeutic frameworks, such as humanistic therapy, are particularly underrepresented in current research applications.",
    "Traditionally, LLM-based psychotherapy tools have addressed assessment, diagnosis, and treatment separately.",
